Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_precision_power(25.10)                    report_precision_power(25.10)

Name
       report_precision_power

Syntax
       report_precision_power <integer >

       Default: 3

       Controls  the  number  of  digits  appearing after the decimal point in
       power values in the timing report output.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

